{"tid":1117092,"cid":25,"subCid":0,"title":"貓仔絕育後傷口輕微滲血","createTime":"2019-04-20T12:29:13.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-21T18:21:51.000Z","uid":67259,"like":3,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"1e649a6d45736111a1f74a499e6b4c79196fc6fe","tid":1117092,"uid":67259,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-20T12:29:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JA9QTYK.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJA9QTYK.jpg&h=8c62d049&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n今日帶左貓仔去做絕育手術 四點幾接左佢返屋企 但係佢好似唔攰咁不斷走黎走去 而家望落個傷口好似有少少滲血 請問係唔係我過分擔心？"},{"pid":"0dd8c5c301720a339d9d90c7eeef79804c6198cc","tid":1117092,"uid":40470,"like":11,"dislike":1,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-20T12:57:58.000Z","msg":"你擔心自己仲好<br />\n<br />\n隻貓諗緊方法向你報切蛋蛋既仇"},{"pid":"ff78b2af584dc86371d4052c382289b7829ef01a","tid":1117092,"uid":67259,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"0dd8c5c301720a339d9d90c7eeef79804c6198cc","tid":1117092,"uid":40470,"like":11,"dislike":1,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-20T12:57:58.000Z","msg":"你擔心自己仲好<br />\n<br />\n隻貓諗緊方法向你報切蛋蛋既仇"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-20T13:48:10.000Z","msg":"佢已經開始咬緊我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f3e66eac16f934f14a227e1a1708972f3087804d","tid":1117092,"uid":19873,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-20T15:47:12.000Z","msg":"第一日？<br />\n頭幾日有少少血滲正常的<br />\n我隻仔上個月尾做完<br />\n頭幾日都有少少血滲，因為無鏠針的<br />\n但之後無事了<br />\n頭套都唔洗用<br />\n因為獸醫話仔好少可會lum 傷口<br />\n不過驚既，見到佢狂lum就戴返"},{"pid":"a939f2081f9ac0fdd48948b98e75f5ad57e18ce1","tid":1117092,"uid":67259,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"f3e66eac16f934f14a227e1a1708972f3087804d","tid":1117092,"uid":19873,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-20T15:47:12.000Z","msg":"第一日？<br />\n頭幾日有少少血滲正常的<br />\n我隻仔上個月尾做完<br />\n頭幾日都有少少血滲，因為無鏠針的<br />\n但之後無事了<br />\n頭套都唔洗用<br />\n因為獸醫話仔好少可會lum 傷口<br />\n不過驚既，見到佢狂lum就戴返"},"citedBy":0,"repl